\par\plain {\f3\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3> (Understanding, but wishing Evan could stay the night): <!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Cs::4>\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93This is been such a wonderful night. I wish you could sleep over and head out in the morning. I don't mind if you leave extra early. It's Christmas, and you spend that with your family.\u8221\'94<!$Scr_Cs::4>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Evan<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3> (Making excuses.): <!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Cs::4>\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I'd love to. But it's a long drive and I know Liz will want me there early.\u8221\'94<!$Scr_Cs::4>}
